{"title":"加紧生产打击敌人","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"加紧生产打击敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话传到车间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话传到车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间笑声冲破天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝自缚绞索套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们一齐用力拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉呀！拉呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量比天大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们不用手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快换马达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就成自动化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国强盗死的快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民笑哈哈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（国营广播器材厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人　李浚德）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快炼出三座桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒火焰烧炉膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧得炉温高又旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多炼铁来快出钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快炼出三座桥："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座架到金门岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座架到马祖岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座架向台湾去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把同胞来解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（上钢一厂　郑松年）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把工地当战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把工地当战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把铁锤当机枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石子当做美国狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥巴便是蒋匪帮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准它们的脑壳砸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫它们粉身见阎王。（某工地工人　荒洪）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}